snippet: Experts from Malaysia, China and Australia agreed that an extensive survey of the sea floor near Australia’s coast would be done by a Chinese Navy vessel.
abstract: Malaysian government says that a Chinese vessel will survey ocean floor at last suspected location of Malaysia Airlines Flight 370.
lead_paragraph: Experts from Malaysia, China and Australia agreed that an extensive survey of the sea floor near Australia’s coast would be done by a Chinese Navy vessel.

headline.main: Chinese Vessel Will Map Ocean Floor in Search for Missing Jet
headline.print_headline: Malaysia: Chinese Vessel to Map Sea Floor in Hunt for Missing Jet
